						<div class="postbody">Hi,
<br />
<br />I've got a French PAL NES and I'm trying to hook it up a computer (I've got no real TV) . I've been told French NES only output RGB. Would there be a quite simple hack to get composite out of the NES ? The PPU is a 2C07. 
<br />
<br />Thanks for your help !
<br />Alex</div>

